与罗莎莉亚 (Rosalía) 在科切拉舞台上表演。图片来源：弗雷泽·哈里森/盖蒂" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Rosalia-and-Rauw-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Rosalia-and-Rauw-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Rosalia-and-Rauw-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Rosalia-and-Rauw-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Rosalia-and-Rauw-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Rosalia-and-Rauw-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/rosalia">罗莎莉亚</a>和劳夫·亚历杭德罗证实，他们已经结束了恋爱关系，并在在一起三年多后取消了订婚。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rosalia-deluxe-edition-motomami-four-previously-unreleased-tracks-3307115">罗莎莉亚 – “Motomami”评论：来自左外野策划者的令人兴奋的发球</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://people.com/rosalia-rauw-alejandro-end-engagement-exclusive-7565061" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《人物》杂志</a>于 7 月 25 日星期二宣布了分手消息。第二天，亚历杭德罗在他的官方 Twitter 帐户和 Instagram 故事上发布了一份声明，证实了这一消息。</p><p> “这些年来，你们一直是我职业成就的一部分，也是我与伴侣一起度过的所有快乐时光的一部分。我从来没有想过自己必须就一件对我来说如此私密的事情发表公开声明，”他在声明中说道。 </p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="qme" dir="ltr"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f494.png" alt="💔" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/270c-1f3fc.png" alt="✌🏼" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://t.co/p5IkAKYksL">pic.twitter.com/p5IkAKYksL</a></p><p> - RAULEETO (@rauwalejandro) <a href="https://twitter.com/rauwalejandro/status/1684305944656609284?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 7 月 26 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p></p><p>他继续说道：“是的，几个月前，罗西和我结束了我们的婚约。有成千上万的问题可能导致分手，但在我们的例子中，并不是因为不忠或第三者。在我消化这一切的这段时间里，错误的公开指控不断出现，出于对她、我们的家人和我们所经历的一切的尊重，我无法保持沉默，继续眼睁睁地看着他们试图摧毁我们的家园。上帝让我经历的最真实的爱情故事。”</p><p>声明最后，亚历杭德罗感谢他的粉丝，并表达了他对他们支持他的爱和感激。</p><p>罗莎莉亚和亚历杭德罗于 2021 年 8 月首次交往，一个月后公开了他们的关系。</p><p>音乐家们之前曾合作过彼此的作品。 Alejandro co-wrote &#39;Chicken Teriyaki&#39; from Rosalía&#39;s album <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/rosalia-motomami-review-an-electrifying-serve-3185409">&#39;Motomami</a> &#39;, and she joined him on a tracks for hos 2022 EP &#39;Trap Cake, Vol. 2&#39; and his third LP &#39;Saturno&#39;. </p><figure id="attachment_3474254" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3474254" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3474254" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Rosalia-and-Rauw.jpg" alt="Rauw Alejandro and Rosalía are seen leaving Craig's on April 18, 2023 in Los Angeles, California. Credit: MEGA/GETTY" width="2000" height="2553" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Rosalia-and-Rauw.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Rosalia-and-Rauw-400x511.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Rosalia-and-Rauw-800x1021.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Rosalia-and-Rauw-696x888.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Rosalia-and-Rauw-1392x1777.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Rosalia-and-Rauw-1068x1363.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3474254" class="wp-caption-text"> Rauw Alejandro and Rosalía are seen leaving Craig&#39;s on April 18, 2023 in Los Angeles, California. Credit: MEGA/GETTY</figcaption></figure><p> Earlier this year, the pair <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rosalia-and-rauw-alejandro-announce-new-collaborative-ep-rr-3413112">announced their first collaborative EP &#39;RR</a> &#39;. They <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rosalia-and-rauw-alejandro-reveal-engagement-in-romantic-new-beso-video-watch-3419831">announced their engagement</a> in the music video for the song &#39;Beso&#39;.</p><p> In other news, Rosalía recently ended <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rosalia-unveils-details-of-huge-world-tour-buy-tickets-3207060">her &#39;Motomami&#39; world tour,</a> in Paris. It was revealed that she had played to a cumulative audience of nearly two million people throughout her entire world tour.</p><p> In <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/rosalia-live-in-lisbon-review-setlist-photos-3356703">a five-star review of Rosalía&#39;s show in Lisbon</a> last November, <em>NME</em> wrote: “Rapidly switching from soaring ballads to industrial club moments, this show is a demonstration of Rosalía&#39;s singular artistic vision.</p><p> “Encompassing the genre-shifting nature of &#39;Motomami&#39; and allowing each of the record&#39;s sides to shine in equal measure – be that with a complex dance routine, or a tear-jerking moment of catharsis – it&#39;s indicative of Rosalía&#39;s sheer talent as a performer, and a reminder that nobody is doing it quite like her at the moment.”</p><p></p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rosalia-and-rauw-alejandro-end-engagement-i-could-not-remain-silent-and-continue-to-watch-as-they-try-to-destroy-the-most-real-love-story-that-god-has-allowed-me-to-experience-3474239">Rosalía and Rauw Alejandro end engagement: “I could not remain silent and continue to watch as they try to destroy the most real love story that God has allowed me to experience”</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
